   &UR; ENTERTAINMENT &LR;  (Moved in ``e'' category)
</P>
<P>
   BEMELMANS-WEB (Undated) _ A Website and a new book devoted to
the art of Ludwig Bemelmans. By Eden Ross Lipson.
</P>
<P>
   ALISTAIR-COOKE (New York) _ A talk with Alistair Cooke,
sprightly at 91. By Frank J. Prial.
</P>
<P>
   CHINA-PEONY-PAVILION (Shanghai, China) _ Arts Abroad: China does
its own official ``Peony Pavilion.'' By Seth Faison.
</P>
<P>
   GAMBLING-BOOK-REVIEW (Undated) _ ``Double Down: Reflections on
Gambling and Loss,'' by Frederick and Steven Barthelme (Houghton
Mifflin). Reviewed by Christopher Lehmann-Haupt.
</P>
